message.body: Heey. How are u? I know it has been awhile
Hey! Its has been awhile lol.. im doing alright how about you?
I know lol. And i am fine. I think we should get together soon
Yea that would be cool. Let me when you're available, this month is a busy month for me but im sure we can definitely figure it out
I am free most weekends. And cool
Ok, I work my one job mon through sat during the day then my sec job thurs thru sunday at night lol so my schedule is a little complicated
That's fine, I get done work about 730 though. Is that okay?
Yes that is fine we will figure something out
